sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant Now as NowScreen
    participant TS as TrackingSession
    participant Prefs as SharedPreferences
    participant Tick as 1Hz Ticker
    participant DB as Room DB

    Note over U,DB: 启动 → 选 Task → 开始 → 暂停/继续 → 停止 → 保存

    U->>Now: tap task row "Coding"
    Now->>TS: start(taskId=42, "Coding")
    TS->>TS: startMs = now
    TS->>Prefs: flush(start, taskId, name)
    Now->>Tick: launch 1Hz coroutine

    loop every second
        Tick->>Now: nowMs = System.currentTimeMillis()
        Now->>TS: elapsedMs(nowMs)
        TS-->>Now: (now - startMs) - pauseAcc
    end

    U->>Now: tap Pause
    Now->>TS: togglePause()
    TS->>TS: pausedAtMs = now
    TS->>Prefs: flush(pausedAt)

    U->>Now: tap Resume
    Now->>TS: togglePause()
    TS->>TS: pauseAcc += now - pausedAtMs
    TS->>Prefs: flush(pauseAcc, pausedAt=null)

    U->>Now: tap Stop
    Now->>TS: stopAndConsume()
    TS-->>Now: StopSnapshot(start, end, note, taskId, pauseAcc)
    TS->>Prefs: clear()
    Now->>DB: insertEventWithAllocations(Event, [Alloc(taskId)])
    DB-->>Now: success
    Now->>Now: render Idle state
